{"tid":1389815,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民612基金: 將盡力向義士提供經濟支援","createTime":"2019-07-31T03:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T12:17:59.000Z","uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"22e7741b30e60368bfc2c62e3a797214073ff773","tid":1389815,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:53:16.000Z","msg":"邊夠錢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp; 612基金而家只有約1200萬，肯定未足以幫哂咁多義士。（單係一位被捕義士既法律費用，都可能接近100萬。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/posts/390688221631348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F612Fund%2Fposts%2F390688221631348&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij7is81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=c2c90d43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/posts/390688221631348</a><br />\n<br />\n612人道支援基金 612 Humanitarian Relief Fund<br />\n昨天 04:48 發佈 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n各位，<br />\n<br />\n知道好多朋友好擔心星期六日（七月27、28日）被捕朋友的情況。其實，由星期六晚到現在，各被捕支援熱線及義務律師團隊，都忙碌於接收個案及相關查詢，以及於警署跟進被捕者情況。（呢幾日支援的朋友好似冇乜點瞓過覺😅🙏🏼 而大家忙於跟進，未有特意公佈相關情況，還請大家見諒。）<br />\n<br />\n今早於粉嶺裁判法院提堂之被告，亦已有律師跟進，請大家繼續關注他們的情況。今早九時亦有社工之聲援行動。<br />\n<br />\n基金這數天也忙碌於處理各種個案，包括醫療、情緒、法律及被捕支援，並儘快為相關朋友安排所需服務。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後，大家關注到運動中的年輕參與者所面對的經濟壓力，我們懇請有需要的朋友聯絡我們，基金在了解情況後，會認真商議並儘力提供可行的支援。🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼</strong><br />\n<br />\nwhatsapp / telegram / 打電話來9845-6641 傾吓啦～<br />\n<br />\n大家加油，保重！<br />\n<br />\n❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤❤️<br />\n<br />\n612人道支援基金<br />\n<br />\n為因反送中運動受傷、被捕或相關人士，提供人道支援，包括醫療、心理/精神，法律及其他有關援助。"},{"pid":"f8825565f446f9a8d7c1c6b3425da799724b8f19","tid":1389815,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"612基金與星火都唔夠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab493e47c41f31bbf81dd80ecd43da34dd96ed44","tid":1389815,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e18dd5001dc6b1cf8aed4925255f01747ff4ef","tid":1389815,"uid":28387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:10:48.000Z","msg":"課金，係時候做野啦各位冷氣軍師"},{"pid":"92c33146344912c7f91d707b119aaa379fbcd0a4","tid":1389815,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a4bff429fd4e289a0635b454a48058c881868c","tid":1389815,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"85<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faf177a058645daad8237b9a32d2c2b310f702e","tid":1389815,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:01:08.000Z","msg":"已課612 而且已廣傳"},{"pid":"1d0325830e755604167ae27f59486dc3d1700056","tid":1389815,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e799b0e65142a782f2817af3fcaafbee2a5bb6","tid":1389815,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}